{"lemma":"رِقَّة","slug":"رِقَّة","root":"ر.ق.ق","root_slug":"ر-ق-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-ق-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n16275","n16276"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%82%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of رَقَّ (raqqa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/riq.qa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n16275","headword_ar":"رَقَّةٌ","root":"rq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Any land by the side of a valley, over which the water spreads in the days of the increase, and into which it then sinks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disappears,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and which therefore produces good herbage:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riqaAqN","text_ar":"رِقَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqaAqN","text_ar":"رَقَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n16276","headword_ar":"رِقَّةٌ","root":"rq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~a","text_ar":"رَقَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in several senses, as shown above, in the first paragraph of this art.]: it is explained in the K as"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diq~apN","text_ar":"دِقَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": [see 1, first sentence:] but El-Munáwee says, in the “ Tow- keef, ” that the former is like the latter [as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thinness"},{"kind":"text","text":"], but that the latter is said with regard to the lateral parts of a thing, and the former"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with regard to the depth"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the extent between the two opposite surfaces"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof]: thus, in a material substance, such, for instance, as a garment, or piece of cloth, [&c.,] it is ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thinness"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"little thickness in comparison with the breadth and length together; littleness in extent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"depth, between the two opposite surfaces: fineness, delicateness, flimsiness, unsubstantialness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uncompactness, in texture &c.:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaxaAnapN","text_ar":"ثَخَانَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SafaAqapN","text_ar":"صَفَاقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) [in water, and sand, &c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shallowness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"littleness of depth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruq~N","text_ar":"رُقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) in mud, and anything imperfectly liquid,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thinness"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"want of spissitude: an attenuated state"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything.] ―         -b2-  Also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Weakness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh;) as in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riq~apu","text_ar":"رِقَّةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAnibK","text_ar":"جَانِبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weakness of resistance;"},{"kind":"text","text":"similar to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liynu","text_ar":"لِينُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAnibK","text_ar":"جَانِبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gilaZu jaAnibK","text_ar":"غِلَظُ جَانِبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (Ham p. 631;) [and in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riq~apu diynK","text_ar":"رِقَّةُ دِينٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weakness of religion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqiyqN","text_ar":"رَقِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abjectness, meanness, paltriness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contemptibleness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weak-heartedness, and fearfulness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see 1:)] and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shame, shyness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bashfulness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b3-  Also (assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Tender-heartedness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqiyqN","text_ar":"رَقِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^araq~u","text_ar":"اَرَقُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mercy, compassion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riq~apu qalobK","text_ar":"رِقَّةُ قَلْبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hn","text_ar":"حن"},{"kind":"text","text":":) in the soul, it is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jafowapN","text_ar":"جَفْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qasowapN","text_ar":"قَسْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (ElMunáwee, TA.) ―         -b4-  [And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Softness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tenderness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easiness and sweetness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elegance, gracefulness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ornateness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of speech: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqiyqN","text_ar":"رَقِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and see also 2. ―         -b5-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Slenderness, softness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gentleness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of voice.] ―         -b6-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Evilness"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"narrowness of the circumstances"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of state or condition: so in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eajibotu mino qil~api maAlihi wariq~api HaAlihi","text_ar":"عَجِبْتُ مِنْ قِلَّةِ مَالِهِ وَرِقَّةِ حَالِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I wondered at the paucity of his property, and the evilness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the narrowness of the circumstances, of his state"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b7-  [And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Scantiness"},{"kind":"text","text":"of living or sustenance &c.] ―         -b8-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riq~apu baTonK","text_ar":"رِقَّةُ بَطْنٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A looseness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"diarrhœa"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xlf","text_ar":"خلف"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["TA"]}]}}